<sect1 id="obtaining">
    <title >Obtaining <application class="software">JMathLib</application ></title >
    <para>The latest release of <application class="software">JMathLib</application > can be obtained 
         from the Sourceforge site.</para>

<para>
Checkout the website at <ulink url="http://mathlib.sourceforge.net">JMathLib</ulink>
</para>
<para>
  <inlinemediaobject>
    <imageobject>
      <imagedata fileref="jmathlib_website_01.gif" format="GIF" width="80%"/>
    </imageobject>
  </inlinemediaobject>
</para>
<para>
  and click on <ulink url="http://mathlib.sourceforge.net/download.php">Download</ulink>
</para>

        <para>Also the latest development version can be downloaded using anonymous cvs</para>            
        <para>use the following commands</para>
        <para><command>cvs -d:pserver:anomynous@cvs.mathlib.sourceforge.net:/cvsroot/mathlib login</command></para>
        <para><command>cvs -z8 -d:pserver:anomynous@cvs.mathlib.sourceforge.net:/cvsroot/mathlib co mathlib</command></para>
</sect1>
    
