<sect1 id="running">
<title>Running <application class="software">JMathLib</application ></title>

<sect2 id="running_on_windows">
<title>Running JMathLib on Windows</title>
<para> For the Windows version just doubleclick on the JMathLib icon</para>

<para>
  <inlinemediaobject>
    <imageobject>
       <imagedata fileref="windows_icon01.gif" format="GIF" />
    </imageobject>
  </inlinemediaobject>
</para>

<para>run <application class="software">JMathLib</application >:</para>
<para>from the MathLib/classes directory enter
<code>java MathLib.MathLibGUI.GUI</code></para>
<para>There are script files to run <application class="software">MathLib</application > from Windows or Linux</para>            
        <para>just enter
        <command>execute.bat</command>            
            </para>
        <para>options:</para>
        <para><option>-t</option> run in console mode</para>
        <para><option>-width</option> specify the width of the gui window</para>
        <para><option>-height</option> specify the height of the gui window</para>            
        <para>-width and -height cannot be used with -t</para>  
        
        
        
</sect2>

